OL,6,FFormer RTE correspondent Charlie Bird
OL,7,Fhas died aged 74.
OL,9,FThe veteran broadcaster, who had motor
OL,10,Fneurone disease, reported on a variety
OL,11,Fof issues from the Stardust fire
OL,12,Ftragedy in 1981 to the Northern
OL,13,FIreland peace process, and had been
OL,14,Fvocal about his diagnosis.
OL,16,FHe helped raise more than E3.3million
OL,17,Ffor charity in a campaign that saw him
OL,18,Fclimb Croagh Patrick in 2022.
