OL,3,CFormer RTE correspondent Charlie Bird
OL,4,Cdies
OL,6,F"As a journalist and broadcaster for
OL,7,FRTE, Charlie had few peers, memorably
OL,8,Fcovering national and international
OL,9,Fevents such as the peace process, the
OL,10,FSeptember 11 attacks on New York, the
OL,11,FGulf War and the National Irish Bank
OL,12,Fscandal.
OL,14,F"Personable and engaging, Charlie
OL,15,Falways had the public interest at
OL,16,Fheart. He represented public service
OL,17,Fbroadcasting in Ireland at its very
OL,18,Fbest.
