OL,3,CFormer RTE correspondent Charlie Bird
OL,4,Cdies
OL,6,F"Over the past few years, Charlie
OL,7,Fcaptured the public imagination,
OL,8,Fnurturing a true spirit of solidarity
OL,9,Fthrough his Croagh Patrick Climb With
OL,10,FCharlie.
OL,12,F"His message of generosity, friendship
OL,13,Fand simply looking out for each other
OL,14,Fwill long be remembered.
OL,16,F"My sincere condolences to his wife
OL,17,FClaire, children, wider family and
OL,18,Fmany friends and colleagues."
