OL,6,FMr Dooley added that Bird, who was a
OL,7,Fformer chair of the NUJ Dublin
OL,8,FBroadcasting branch, "was passionate
OL,9,Fabout news and had a unique ability to
OL,10,Fdevelop relationships".
OL,12,F"He was stubborn and relentless in
OL,13,Fpursuit of whatever he set out to
OL,14,Fachieve.
OL,16,F"His life should not be defined by his
OL,17,Fillness but by the remarkable
OL,18,Fqualities he displayed in the face of
OL,19,Fadversity. He leaves a remarkable
OL,20,Flegacy."
